Pre-Game Insights: The national teams of Australia and England are currently 1-1, although both the Australians and the British are among the main favorites of the current T20 World Cup.
Australia managed to play two battles with the British in October, and both “the team of three lions” won with the same handicap of eight runs.
England had a good competition with Afghanistan, and Ireland’s defeat looks like an accident that should not happen again.
